overview.en: KAE (Keuoi) is a brand token listed on Ipparts Exchange (IPPAEX). The token is contractually backed by 48% of the Kaeuoi brand value. KAE raises funds for Kaeuoi, a new type of Internet Union.
overview.zh: KAE (Keuoi) 是在 Ipparts Exchange (IPPAEX) 上市的品牌代币。该代币由 Kaeuoi 品牌价值的 48% 提供合同支持。 KAE 为新型互联网联盟 Kaeuoi 筹集资金.
